videos.description: Duane Wilson steals and takes it all the way to the rim for a nice one-handed dunk in the first half against Arizona.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Wilson takes it coast-to-coast for the slam

videos.description: Admon Gilder steals and takes it up the court but he's rejected by Deandre Ayton who swats it away.
videos.headline: Arizona's Ayton denies Gilder at the rim

videos.description: Alex Barcelle passes to Deandre Ayton who jams it in during the first half against the Aggies.
videos.headline: Ayton throws it down for the Wildcats

videos.description: Duane Wilson steals and takes it all the way to the rim for a nice one-handed dunk in the first half against Arizona.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Wilson takes it coast-to-coast for the slam

videos.description: Robert Williams blocks Parker Jackson-Cartwright's shot and gets it to Duane Wilson who knocks in a nice three at the end of the first half to give Texas A&M the lead against Arizona.
videos.headline: Wilson's triple puts the Aggies ahead at the half

videos.description: Tyler Davis gets by defenders and shows off a nice spin move before putting in the layup against Arizona.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Davis spins and hits

videos.description: JJ Caldwell finds Savion Flagg who puts it in from underneath the basket to tie the game 47-47 against Arizona.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Flagg hits tricky jumper to tie game

videos.description: Admon Gilder drives inside for a nice layup and draws the foul on Arizona's Dylan Smith.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Gilder drives for and -1

videos.description: Parker Jackson-Cartwright drains a sweet three from the corner and beats the shot-clock buzzer in the second half against Texas A&M.
videos.headline: Arizona's Cartwright knocks in huge triple at shot-clock buzzer

videos.description: With Arizona ahead 65-62, Duane Wilson misses a three and gets the foul on Aggies' Deandre Ayton for three free throw attempts with two seconds left on the clock.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Wilson draws foul for 3 shots
